This paper deals with the security and privacy aspects of biometric authentication, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cyber security (cs.CY). The proposed encryption scheme and computational model involve machine learning techniques, which are often discussed in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper also discusses the implementation and evaluation of the proposed scheme, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
